  <entry>
    <title>Hexo搭建</title>
    <url>/2025/05/01/#Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Hexo搭建步骤："><a href="#Hexo搭建步骤：" class="headerlink" title="Hexo搭建步骤："></a>Hexo搭建步骤：</h2><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/sinat_37781304/article/details/82729029">Hexo搭建和命令参考</a></p>
<ol>
<li>下载安装Git和Node.js后，D 盘创建WWW，WWW目录下cmd</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g </span><br><span class="line">hexo init Blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> Blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<ol start="2">
<li><p>创建GitHub仓库: <a href="https://cyphersun.github.io/">https://cyphersun.github.io/</a></p>
</li>
<li><p>链接GitHub，然后确认</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;CypherSun&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;84860748@qq.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git config user.name</span><br><span class="line">git config user.email</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<ol start="4">
<li>创建SSH文件，一直回车就行</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">&quot;84860748@qq.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<ol start="5">
<li><p>在GitHub的Setting中，找到SSH keys，点击New SSH key，输入在本地生成的id_rsa.pub，不是id_rsa，两个别弄错了</p>
</li>
<li><p>输入yes，确定链接GitHub</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<ol start="7">
<li>Blog目录下cmd</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-renderer-less hexo-renderer-ejs</span><br><span class="line">npm i hexo-theme-async@latest</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-helper-live2d</span><br><span class="line">npm install live2d-widget-model-wanko</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<ol start="8">
<li><p>复制备份的scaffolds，source，_config.yml，_config.async.yml，package.json到Blog目录下</p>
</li>
<li><p>访问本地：<br>hexo clean<br>hexo g<br>hexo s<br>访问本地 <a href="http://localhost:4000/">4000 端口</a></p>
</li>
<li><p>上传Github：<br>hexo clean<br>hexo g<br>hexo d<br>npm run a<br>访问 <a href="https://cyphersun.github.io/">Github 网址</a></p>
</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>重要</category>
      </categories>
